## Key Composables

### API Layer (`composables/api/`)
- `useN2YO.ts` ‚Äî pass predictions, real-time positions via N2YO proxy
- `useSpaceTrack.ts` ‚Äî login + TLE fetch via `/api/space-track` proxy
- `useTLEData.ts` ‚Äî TLE orchestration: Space-Track first, CelesTrak fallback
- `useSatnogs.ts` ‚Äî transponder/frequency data
- `useSatelliteSearch.ts` ‚Äî satellite name/NORAD search

### Pass Predict (`composables/pass-predict/`)
- `usePassData.ts` ‚Äî fetch + store pass list
- `usePassStatus.ts` ‚Äî is pass active/upcoming/past
- `useRealTimePosition.ts` ‚Äî polls N2YO during active pass
- `useSatellitePath.ts` ‚Äî arc path calculation for SVG polar plot
- `usePolarPlotBackground.ts` ‚Äî static background SVG (circles, labels)
- `usePassFiltering.ts` ‚Äî filter by satellite, elevation etc.
- `usePassCleanup.ts` ‚Äî cleanup timers/intervals

### Storage (`composables/storage/`)
- `useSettings.ts` ‚Äî app settings: location, preferences (IndexedDB)
- `useIndexedDB.ts` ‚Äî IndexedDB CRUD wrapper
- `useSecureStorage.ts` ‚Äî AES-encrypted credential storage

### AR Tracking
- `useDeviceOrientation.ts` ‚Äî wraps `DeviceOrientationEvent`:
  - `alpha` = compass heading 0‚Äì360¬∞ (True North)
  - `beta` = pitch -180 to 180¬∞
  - `gamma` = roll -90 to 90¬∞
  - iOS 13+ requires explicit permission ‚Äî handled internally
- `components/ar-track/ArPolarPlot.vue` ‚Äî SVG polar plot rotated by compass so "up = where you're pointing"
- `components/ar-track/ArIndicators.vue` ‚Äî EL/AZ overlay indicators

### Other Composables
- `useCredentials.ts` ‚Äî manages API keys (read/write to secure storage)
- `useSoundAlerts.ts` ‚Äî audio alerts when satellite is overhead
- `usePWAInstall.ts` ‚Äî PWA install prompt handling

