## Code Style Rules

### Vue
- Always `<script setup lang="ts">` ‚Äî never plain `<script setup>` (breaks TS syntax)
- Composables over options API, always
- File names: `kebab-case.vue` for components, `camelCase.ts` for composables

### TypeScript
- No `any` ‚Äî use `unknown` or proper types
- Always type function params and returns
- Use interfaces for data shapes, type aliases for unions

### GPS / Location
- `enableHighAccuracy` respects user setting
- Timeout: 30000ms (not 10000 ‚Äî GPS cold start needs time)
- maximumAge: 60000ms (accept 1-min cached fix, much faster)
- Fallback retry: low accuracy + 300000ms maximumAge if first attempt fails

### UnoCSS
- Pure utility classes ‚Äî no `@apply`
- Custom shortcuts in `uno.config.ts` for repeated patterns
- Color palette: `space-*` (dark backgrounds), `primary-*` (accent)

