## DO's and DON'Ts

**ALWAYS:**
- `<script setup lang="ts">` on every Vue component
- Use `class/gp` for Space-Track TLE queries (never `tle_latest`)
- GPS timeout = 30000, maximumAge = 60000
- Work in feature or development worktree, never in satTrack.git

**NEVER:**
- `@apply` in CSS
- Work directly in `satTrack.git/`
- Merge feature branch directly to `main`
- Create git tags manually (CI does it)
- Use `tle_latest`, `tle`, or `tle_publish` on Space-Track API
